import jax
import jax.numpy as jnp

def generated_fn(x0, x1, x2):
    v0 = jnp.multiply(x2, x0)
    v1 = jnp.maximum(x1, x0)
    v2 = jnp.maximum(v0, x2)
    v3 = jnp.cos(x0)
    v4 = jnp.add(x0, v0)
    v5 = jnp.subtract(x2, v3)
    v6 = jnp.subtract(v5, v1)
    v7 = jnp.subtract(v0, v0)
    v8 = jnp.multiply(v5, v7)
    return v8
